'KF003',150,'2012-05-24 10:10:15',3,NULL,'0','1','','',''),(402,4,44,1,'Orchid Flower','Orchid-Flower','Thailand-Orchid.jpg','Thailand-Orchid.jpg','Thailand-Orchid.jpg','Thailand-Orchid.jpg,ascocentrum_ampulaceum.jpg,bamboo_orchid.jpg,beallara_purplepassion.jpg,dorisia_sunset.jpg,Orchid-1.jpg,Orchid-2.jpg,Orchid-Flower-3.jpg','<p><br />There are about 25,000 to 30,000 known species of orchids around the world. Orchids are found in all continents except Antarctica, from hot tropical jungles to the cold climate inNorth America. However, some orchids are&nbsp; found only in certain region of the world and nowhere else, for example, the Vanda genus colonizes onlySouth East Asia. Orchids are often seen in flower arrangements because there are so many different types and they add color to any bouquet.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>','OF004',780,'2012-05-24 10:12:51',4,NULL,'0','1','','',''),(403,4,44,1,'Aparajita( Indigo flower)','Aparajita-Indigo-flower-','Aparajita-3.jpg','Aparajita-3.jpg','Aparajita-3.jpg','Aparajita-1.jpg,Aparajita-2.jpg,Aparajita-3.jpg,Aparajita-4.jpg,Aparajita-5.jpg,Aparajita-6.jpg,Aparajita-7.jpg,Aparajita-8.jpg','<span><br />These&nbsp;flowers&nbsp;bloom plentifully in rainy season and have<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>attractive,&nbsp;beautiful stems and flowers on these stems are star-shaped. Main color is vavy blue and other colors are seen such as violet,&nbsp;white and off-white. Main reason of their popularity is their attractive and deep&nbsp;colors.&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</span>','AP005',490,'2012-05-24 10:23:57',5,NULL,'0','1','','',''),(404,4,45,1,'Snapdragon Flower','Snapdragon-Flower','Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg','Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg','Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg','Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg,snapdragon-flowers-assorted.jpg,define-snapdragon-4.jpg,Snapdragon_flower-1.jpg,Snapdragon_flower-2.jpg','<p><strong><br />Snapdragons</strong> bloom plentifully in summer season and have attractive and refreshing colors like purple, red, yellow and white.<em><strong> </strong></em><strong>Snapdragon</strong>&nbsp;is an annual flower that children love because they can snap open the flowers like puppets. Snapdragons endure cool weather . In many occasions these flowers are used &nbsp;to use &nbsp;flower arrangements and are sold as&nbsp;bouquets in the markets.<br /> <br /> <strong>Scientific name:</strong>&nbsp;<em><u>Antirrhinum</u></em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><u>majus<br /><br /></u></em></p>','SF001',890,'2012-05-24 10:31:07',1,'194,401','0','1','','',''),(405,4,45,1,'Dahlia Flower','Dahlia-Flower','Pink_Dahlia.jpg','Pink_Dahlia.jpg','Pink_Dahlia.jpg','flower-pink-dahlia.jpg,Pink_Dahlia.jpg,Dahlia.jpg,dahlia-flower-cerise.jpg','<p><strong><br />Dahlias</strong> are classified according to flower shape and arrangement of petals. They have a wide height range (1 to 6 ft) and a variety of flower shapes and sizes (2 to 12 inches). Color range includes orange, pink, purple, red, scarlet, yellow, and white.&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;<em><strong></strong></em></p>','DF002',190,'2012-05-24 10:33:36',2,NULL,'0','1','','',''),(406,4,45,1,'Gladiolus Flower','Gladiolus-Flower','gladiolus-flower_24.jpg','gladiolus-flower_24.jpg','gladiolus-flower_24.jpg','gladiolus-pic.jpg,pinkflowersgladiolus.jpg,gladioli-euphorbia.jpg,gladiolus-1.jpg,gladiolus.jpg,Gladiolus-Espresso.jpg,gladiolus-flower-5.jpg,gladiolus-flower_24.jpg','<p><span><br />These&nbsp;flowers&nbsp;bloom plentifully in&nbsp;summer&nbsp;season and have<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>attractive,&nbsp;beautiful stems and flowers on these stems are star-shaped. They come in varieties of colors including red, green, yellow and blue. Main reason of their popularity is their attractive and elegant colors. These flowers not only add beauty to your garden but are also used in making bouquets and floral arrangements.&nbsp;Its market demands quite well.<br /><br />&nbsp;</span><strong></strong></p>','GF003',560,'2012-05-24 10:37:35',3,'187','0','1','',''