apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>(<strong>T shirt</strong><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>or<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>tee</strong>) is a style of<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span>shirt</span>. A T-shirt is button less and collarless, usually with short sleeves and frequently a round neck line. T-shirts are typically made of cotton fibers (sometimes others). T-shirts can be decorated with text and/or pictures, and they are often used to advertise , promoting products, companies, films and websites. T-shirt fashions include many styles for both men and women, and for all age groups, including baby, youth, teen, adult and elderly sizes.</span></p>','TS004',570,'2012-05-24 12:56:23',4,'416','0','1','','',''),(419,4,40,1,'Tie','Tie','Stripe-Tie.jpg','Stripe-Tie.jpg','Stripe-Tie.jpg','Bow-tie.jpg,Custom-tie.JPG,Interview-Business-Ties.jpg,Print-tie.jpg,silk-twill-bunny-printed-tie.jpg,stripe_tie.jpg,Stripe-Bow-Tie.jpg,Stripe-Tie.jpg','<p><span><br />Men can wear different types of ties including formal ties or bow ties with their shirts. For wedding Ceremonies bow ties are most used. Formal ties are most used in office and any party and most used in winter season in each country. Ties are made of cotton fibers or others and decorated with stripe, boll print or plain color etc.<br />&nbsp;</span></p>','TE005',1000,'2012-05-24 01:01:41',5,NULL,'0','1','','',''),(420,4,41,1,'Sari','Sari','Jamdani_Saree.jpg','Jamdani_Saree.jpg','Jamdani_Saree.jpg','Gray-Pillar-1.jpg,Jamdani_Saree -Red-Black.jpg,Jamdani_Saree.jpg,KATAN-SILK-JAMDANI-SAREE.jpg,Pictures-of-pure-cotton-saree.jpg,plain-ivory-color-cotton-saree.jpg,SilkSareecombines.jpg','<p>A&nbsp;<strong>sari</strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>saree</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>is a strip of unstitched cloth, worn by females, ranging from four to nine yards in length that is draped over the body in various styles.&nbsp;It is popular inIndia, &nbsp;Banglade